1
00:00:04,727 --> 00:00:08,853
We praise God and we bear witness that there is only one God.

2
00:00:08,853 --> 00:00:10,742
The one true God who created all of us.

3
00:00:14,378 --> 00:00:23,925
We've been fortunate to receive a message from God

4
00:00:23,925 --> 00:00:29,561
that is proven with tangible evidence, physical evidence for the first time in history.

5
00:00:29,561 --> 00:00:37,016
Something that the world is going to recognize, maybe it will take the world 20 years or 50 years.

6
00:00:37,016 --> 00:00:48,327
But we are fortunate to be the first pioneers who see this evidence and realize what God is telling us.

7
00:00:48,327 --> 00:00:56,257
There is a definite message from God to all of us, giving us the most vital information that we need.

8
00:00:56,257 --> 00:01:01,642
And I will try to draw a picture of the whole thing in this KHUTBAH

9
00:01:01,642 --> 00:01:07,698
to summarize for all of us the things that we've been witnessing for the last few years,

10
00:01:07,698 --> 00:01:14,174
and also for our guests to catch up with this... a summary of the whole thing.

11
00:01:14,174 --> 00:01:19,660
God created us and He did not leave us without support.

12
00:01:19,660 --> 00:01:23,883
He didn't just leave us in the wild without direction or guidance.

13
00:01:23,883 --> 00:01:31,893
He did quite a few things to help us attain our objective

14
00:01:31,893 --> 00:01:36,000
which is one of the things that most people don't know.

15
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,451
People in the street, they don't know what our objective is.

16
00:01:38,451 --> 00:01:49,649
So, God sent messages and messengers and told us exactly the things that we need.

17
00:01:49,649 --> 00:01:52,446
The first thing that God did was

18
00:01:52,446 --> 00:01:57,358
that He gathered all of us, all the human beings

19
00:01:57,358 --> 00:02:00,650
who came to this earth and will come to this earth

20
00:02:00,650 --> 00:02:04,094
and that was before creation of the Heavens and the Earth,

21
00:02:04,094 --> 00:02:08,970
and He had us witness, bear witness that He alone is our Lord,

22
00:02:08,970 --> 00:02:11,611
that we'll worship God alone.

23
00:02:13,569 --> 00:02:17,396
God called all the people, said, "do you bear witness that I am your Lord?"

24
00:02:17,396 --> 00:02:18,000
And we said "yes."

25
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:23,458
So, this constitutes natural instinct in each one of us.

26
00:02:23,458 --> 00:02:28,820
So, each one of us comes to this world, we are born with a natural instinct to worship God alone,

27
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:32,577
and not to worship or idolize anybody else.

28
00:02:32,577 --> 00:02:39,301
We are born... born with the knowledge and recognition that God is the One who created us,

29
00:02:39,301 --> 00:02:41,103
that He's the One who provides for us.

30
00:02:41,103 --> 00:02:44,041
He decides exactly how many dollars we're going to get.

31
00:02:45,803 --> 00:02:51,540
And God is the One who terminates our life when the specific time comes.

32
00:02:51,540 --> 00:02:53,608
And God is the One who will resurrect us

33
00:02:53,608 --> 00:02:57,959
and God is the One who will put us in Heaven or Hell depending on our work.

34
00:02:57,959 --> 00:03:01,615
Therefore, we must owe our allegiance to God alone

35
00:03:01,615 --> 00:03:03,509
and not to any creature.

36
00:03:03,509 --> 00:03:08,030
So, this is one of the important things that God did for us.

37
00:03:08,030 --> 00:03:14,650
So, what does the average human being need out there in the street? The average person?

38
00:03:16,077 --> 00:03:20,112
The most vital information that first and foremost is "who are you?"

39
00:03:20,112 --> 00:03:25,011
God tells us in this mathematically coded message who we are.

40
00:03:25,011 --> 00:03:28,709
Ask the average person out there "who are you?"

41
00:03:28,709 --> 00:03:30,709
And they will look in the mirror.

42
00:03:30,947 --> 00:03:33,887
Which is wrong.

43
00:03:33,887 --> 00:03:35,628
Because they think this is us.

44
00:03:38,901 --> 00:03:44,879
We come to realize now that each one of us consists of two entities,

45
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:47,494
distinct entities: a body and a soul.

46
00:03:47,494 --> 00:03:50,636
And then the soul is the real person,

47
00:03:50,636 --> 00:03:52,870
that the body is not the person.

48
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:55,430
The body is a garment that we are wearing.

49
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:57,478
So, that's who we are.

50
00:03:57,478 --> 00:03:59,210
How many people out there know this?

51
00:03:59,210 --> 00:04:06,358
They have to read God's message with the tangible physical evidence and realize who we are.

52
00:04:06,358 --> 00:04:08,211
Actually this is an easy matter.

53
00:04:08,211 --> 00:04:11,273
You can logically prove it to anyone.

54
00:04:11,273 --> 00:04:14,037
They realize this body is not us.

55
00:04:14,037 --> 00:04:18,812
They realize there's a difference between a living person and a dead person.

56
00:04:18,812 --> 00:04:25,743
The dead person that is not moving, still, does not have a person in it.

57
00:04:25,743 --> 00:04:27,841
It's just a body, a garment.

58
00:04:27,841 --> 00:04:29,785
Something is gone.

59
00:04:29,785 --> 00:04:36,206
And this leads to some very important facts.

60
00:04:36,206 --> 00:04:41,534
One fact is, I gave my body breakfast, lunch and dinner yesterday.

61
00:04:41,534 --> 00:04:43,681
What did I give myself?

62
00:04:43,681 --> 00:04:50,350
And this makes us realize that the real person is probably starving.

63
00:04:50,350 --> 00:04:54,737
The real person needs breakfast, lunch and dinner.

64
00:04:54,737 --> 00:05:00,610
And this is provided in the message that God sent to us.

65
00:05:00,610 --> 00:05:07,381
So, this is the first, one of the first items. Who we are? And now we know.

66
00:05:07,381 --> 00:05:15,296
The second point that the average person doesn't know out there is "Why are we here?"

67
00:05:15,296 --> 00:05:17,066
"What is the whole idea?"

68
00:05:17,066 --> 00:05:21,486
Are we here to go to school and study hard and take tests?

69
00:05:21,486 --> 00:05:26,579
And put up with parents and teachers and colleagues,

70
00:05:26,579 --> 00:05:29,710
And then get out and do some work,

71
00:05:29,710 --> 00:05:33,937
work hard from 8:00 to 5:00, go home, watch the TV and then,

72
00:05:33,937 --> 00:05:38,401
go to sleep, get up in the morning, go to work

73
00:05:38,401 --> 00:05:40,656
back from work, watch the TV,

74
00:05:40,656 --> 00:05:44,950
sleep, get up in the morning, go to work... is this what...I mean

75
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:46,700
Is this what we are here for?

76
00:05:46,700 --> 00:05:49,784
What is the whole idea? Why are we here?

77
00:05:49,784 --> 00:05:54,416
And we know the answer from God's message

78
00:05:54,416 --> 00:05:58,109
that we are here to prepare for the real life

79
00:05:58,109 --> 00:05:59,949
eternal life.

80
00:05:59,949 --> 00:06:03,574
We know that everyone of us is gonna leave here.

81
00:06:03,574 --> 00:06:04,872
We are here temporarily.

82
00:06:04,872 --> 00:06:06,900
Let us say for a 100 years

83
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:11,800
just to be optimistic or pessimistic, anyway you wanna look at it.

84
00:06:13,590 --> 00:06:17,557
If we are here for 100 years, we know that we're gonna go on to something else.

85
00:06:17,557 --> 00:06:19,655
What is this something else?

86
00:06:19,655 --> 00:06:22,725
God tells us what it is, specifically.

87
00:06:22,725 --> 00:06:24,341
And what it looks like.

88
00:06:24,341 --> 00:06:27,399
And how to prepare for it.

89
00:06:32,937 --> 00:06:35,822
What do we need is another question.

90
00:06:35,822 --> 00:06:38,052
What do we really need?

91
00:06:38,052 --> 00:06:42,427
The average person out there is taking care of his or her body.

92
00:06:42,427 --> 00:06:44,007
Whatever the body wants.

93
00:06:44,007 --> 00:06:45,314
The body wants a nice home.

94
00:06:45,314 --> 00:06:47,357
The body wants nice clothes.

95
00:06:47,357 --> 00:06:49,476
The body wants food.

96
00:06:49,476 --> 00:06:52,698
And they are doing that.

97
00:06:52,698 --> 00:06:55,875
But they are totally neglecting the real person.

98
00:06:57,330 --> 00:06:58,893
So, what do we need?

99
00:06:58,893 --> 00:07:01,294
God told us exactly what we need.

100
00:07:03,168 --> 00:07:06,769
God didn't just leave us without support.

101
00:07:06,769 --> 00:07:09,533
He gave us the natural instinct to worship Him. He told us who we are,

102
00:07:09,533 --> 00:07:10,834
why we are here,

103
00:07:10,834 --> 00:07:12,042
where we're going,

104
00:07:12,042 --> 00:07:14,026
