105
00:07:14,026 --> 00:07:21,679
and most importantly, how to attain perfect happiness here and forever.

106
00:07:21,679 --> 00:07:29,036
This is the most illusive goal for the average person out there: Perfect Happiness.

107
00:07:29,176 --> 00:07:32,675
As it turns out, there are lots of problems in this world.

108
00:07:32,675 --> 00:07:35,494
At home, husbands and wives are fighting.

109
00:07:36,865 --> 00:07:41,486
At work, colleagues are fighting with each other. They're jealous of each other. They don't like each other.

110
00:07:44,927 --> 00:07:46,611
Nations at war.

111
00:07:46,611 --> 00:07:49,994
There are lots of problems out there.

112
00:07:49,994 --> 00:07:55,848
