114
00:07:59,795 --> 00:08:03,288
And God tells us exactly how in this message.

115
00:08:03,288 --> 00:08:09,071
We now know the secret of happiness because God told us what it is.

116
00:08:10,218 --> 00:08:12,140
Tooboo Ela Allah, Repent.

